messages.messageBody:
Well the dreaded snaggle tooth that Sierra was harboring finally fell out. All on it's own. She discovered it this morning and found it on the floor by her bed. Sierra made a point to tell me she wants all her teeth to just fall out like that!! So I learned that indeed they will even if no one pulls them!

At least Tara and I don't have to look at that thing hanging there anymore. <BG>

Mary B
